title: Home
---

<div class="[ home ]">
	<header class="[ hero ]">
		<h1 aria-label="Hi, I'm Elly. I like creating delightful, magical, and accessible art with code.">
			<span class="detitlify">Hi, Iâ€™m <stylized-text label="Elly" class="[ logo-inline ]">&lt;e//y&gt;</stylized-text>
			</span>
			<span>I like creating <span class="stroke" style="--color: var(--accent-solid);">delightful</span>, <span class="stroke" style="--color: var(--accent-solid);">magical</span>, and <span class="stroke" style="--color: var(--accent-solid);">accessible</span> art with code<span style="color: var(--accent-solid);">.</span></span>
